Text: Awesome stuff! sounded so good the first time on triple j!

walkinshaw, Excellent upload and quality tune.
For those of you confused, this is the pendulum remix of the Australian Broadcasting Corporations news theme originally written by Peter Wall & Tony Ansell.
Ransley13, it was awesome hearing it for the first time on triple J.
Heard this a few months ago on some blog site and then again on JJJ on Aussie day. This tune always reminds me of when I was a kid and I had to be home before ABC news came on hahah.
